				<textElement markup="html">
					<font fontName="Times New Roman" size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["I am happy to inform you that you have been admitted into the " +"<b>"+" School of " + $F{schoolname} +"</b>"+ "  to pursue a "+"<b>" +$F{degreename}+"</b>" + " in " +"<b>"+ $F{majorname}+"</b>" + " subject to presentation of your original academic certificate for Verification on the day of registration.<br><p>You are expected to report to the University on " + $F{admission_date}+"." + " Kindly visit http://ueab.ac.ke/index/node/83 to access the fee structure. On the registration day you are required to pay the fees before you are registered.  All payments must be made in bankerâ€™s cheque or money order only payable to the University of Eastern Africa, Baraton." +"<br><p>You will be required to abide by the rules and regulations as stipulated in the Student Handbook and the correct Academic Bulletin."+"<p><br>Boarding facilities are available for interested students at a fee as stipulated in the free structure. Borders are advised to come with their own bedding: blankets, bed sheets, pillow and pillowcase and other personal items. A mattress may be purchased at the University Bookstore. Rental facilities are available outside the University for day students.<br></p>" + "<p>Interested students are advised to apply for HELB loans by 30th September 2016. To apply visit www.helb.co.ke for more information.</p>" + "<p>During the orientation week, you will be required to do a full medical checkup at the University Hospital at a cost of Ksh 2500 (Two thousand five hundred shillings only).</p>" +"<p>We look forward to seeing you here as a student and trust that you will find your studies enjoyable and fulfilling in a Christian environment.</p>" +"<p>Yours faithfully,</p>"]]></textFieldExpression>
